#To biu  trn th hin  tui ca cc cu th
x = np.array([Under20['Name'].count(), age20_25['Name'].count(), age25_30['Name'].count(), Above30['Name'].count()])

plt.show()

#Tng s cu th h tr ghi bn mi clb
Assists_by_clubs = pd.DataFrame(epl_df.groupby('Club',as_index=False) ['Assists'].sum()) #groupby ct Club v ct tng s h tr ca mi clb(Assists)
sns.set_theme(style="whitegrid", color_codes=True) #mu
ax = sns.barplot(x='Club',y='Assists', data=Assists_by_clubs.sort_values(by='Assists'),palette='tab10')
ax.set_xlabel('Club',fontsize=30)
ax.set_ylabel('Assists',fontsize=30)
plt.xticks(rotation=75)
plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (20,8)
plt.title('Plot of Clubs vs Total Assists', fontsize=30)

Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Plot of Clubs vs Total Assists')
